[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "準備、完の了！\nいつでもブラオールに行けるっすわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00033",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "今回はまた随分と積荷が少ないのね。\n本当にバーバラ号とアルビ号の２隻で大丈夫なの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00034",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "平気だよ。ブラオールまでの航路は安全だからね。\nなんたって諸島同盟でも一番の大都市だし？　うん平気",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00035",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "今のうちにフロッケ号の手入れができるって\nランツェさんも張り切ってたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00036",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ブラオール、噂に聞いた大都市……\nアルビちゃん、ついに足を踏み入れます……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00037",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "すっかりおのぼりさんだね、オノボリーナ。\n神聖国の案内人ともあろうものが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00038",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "むっ……しょうがないでしょ、\n初めてのブラオールなんだから。あとアルビーナな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00039",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "じゃあ、案内人の役割も僕に任せてもらおうかな？\n何度か僕らは行ったことがあるしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00040",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "とはいえ、最後に行ったのはだいぶ昔のことだ。\n景色もすっかり変わってるかもしれないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00041",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あれ、そういえばリーベとゴゥは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00042",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "あの子らは別件。危険生物の「管理」中だよ。\nその分アタシらが同行させてもらうから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00043",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "同行という指示は我が主から出ていない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00044",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガ、それにキューン！\nまた私たちを監視しているの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00045",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "う、ううん。今回は違うの。\nイェルカ姉貴とシトリンに用があって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00046",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "我が主からの命令。二人も私たちと共に\n不穏分子の「管理」を進めよと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00047",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "アウグスト直々の招集ってことかい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00048",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "不穏分子って……ゴゥさんたちがしてる危険生物の\n「管理」を手伝うって意味じゃ、ないですよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00049",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "肯定。私たちの分担は危険思想を抱く人類、\nたとえば元極夜の錬金党のクリセルダなど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00050",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そんな！　まだクリセルダさんのことを……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00051",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "だね。それを聞かされちゃあ\n仕事をさせるわけにはいかないよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00052",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "クリセルダも最近は大人しくしていると聞くよ。\nそんな急に話を進めることはないと思うけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00053",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そ、それは……事情が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00054",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "私からすれば我が主の命令に従わない姉上が\n同じ兄弟として理解できない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00055",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "こういう「管理」は粋じゃないんだよ。\n彼女をどう裁くかは同じ人間に委ねるべきさ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00056",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "不測の事態が起こった際には、\n実力行使の許可も出ている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00057",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ちょ、ちょっとヤド姉！\n本当に兄弟で戦っちゃうの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00058",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "キューン、下がって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00059",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "あなたがたであれば、私一人で十分と判断",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_036_00060",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ふぅん……言ったね妹め！　やってみるがいいさ！\nやれるものならねッ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00061",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]